Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt

Class DOTypeAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<DataTypeTemplateAdapter,T>
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt.AbstractDataTypeAdapter<TDOType>
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt.DOTypeAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataTemplate, IDTTComparable<TDOType>
public class DOTypeAdapter extends AbstractDataTypeAdapter<TDOType>
A representation of the model object DOType.

The following features are supported:

  1. Adapter
    • Returns the value of the DataTypeTemplateAdapter reference object
    • Returns the value of the DAAdapter reference object By DA name
    • Returns the value of the DOTypeAdapter reference object By SDO name
  2. Principal functions
    • Add TPrivate under this object
    • Returns the value of the TDA reference object By name
    • Returns DataAttributeRef By DaTypeName
    • Returns DataAttributeRef By DoTypeName
    • Returns List Of DataAttributeRef By Custom filter
    • Returns List Of DataAttributeRef By DA Object
    • Returns List of TSDO or TDA
    • Returns the value of the cdc attribute
  3. Checklist functions
    • Compare two TSDO or Two TDA
    • Compare Two TDOType
    • Check and Complete structData from DoTypeName
    • Check whether TDOType contain TDA with Struct Btype By Id
    • Check whether TDOType contain TSDO By Id
    • Check whether TDOType contain TDA By Name
    • Check whether TDOType contain TEnumType By Id
